{"tid":2179171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本TBS新聞 引述香港報章內容「香港警察曾搜查日經新聞分部」","createTime":"2020-08-29T02:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T04:35:02.000Z","uid":56115,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6cca3d2d9be8807d4d3183914269b9bd1b882e","tid":2179171,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"據香港媒體報導，香港民運人士於本月10日周備等人因涉嫌違反《國家安全法》被捕，同日《日經》香港分部也受到警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果日報》等香港報章引述法新社的報導指，3名香港警察調查人員今月10日到日經報香港分社並出示法庭搜查令。涉及1年前《香港眾志》於日經新聞下的一則要求國際社會支持抗爭的意見廣告。<br />\n<br />\n 同日，香港警察以涉嫌違反《國家安全法》拘捕，《蘋果日報》創辦人黎智英及《香港眾志》成員周庭。目前還不清楚他們是否與此事件（日經被搜查）有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tbs.co.jp/newseye/tbs_newseye4064861.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tbs.co.jp%2Fnewseye%2Ftbs_newseye4064861.html&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=a654f4ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tbs.co.jp/newseye/tbs_newseye4064861.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引述嘅香港報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/NWZ2ALN345HWJLEU7RNRJOL62I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FNWZ2ALN345HWJLEU7RNRJOL62I%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zh6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=5f507a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2FNWZ2ALN345HWJLEU7RNRJOL62I%2F&h=7e3dc9d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/NWZ2ALN345HWJLEU7RNRJOL62I/</a>"},{"pid":"596fc6cab91b6b0a57b8d11c6494da572d049e3e","tid":2179171,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c865e2e22b5e2a77da031ee9080eb7eec352fc87","tid":2179171,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 